%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/T%E1%BB%A9-Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/poem-8jAxpZ7sLfJ22hdtNJiJ4Q">Tứ Thẩm Đức Tiềm - 賜沈德潛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-LWiJ3ebJ3gpU86_3bbLouw">Ái Tân Giác La Hoằng Lịch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Vi%C3%AAn-Minh-vi%C3%AAn/poem-vFKM4EqxbQHheoXIOW6LTQ">Viên Minh viên - 圓明園</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i/poem-76D2hQ5sC9u9SnY9R16gFA">Xuất tái - 出塞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
